summary:
SINGING ROCK is one of the world leaders on the market of climbing equipment and professional protective equipment for work at height, military and rescue. Our company is located in the heart of Europe. Most of our staff are climbers and together with our sponsored athletes and professionals we are able to develop, test and improve our high quality climbing and personal protective equipment. 
All our climbing equipment can be shipped worldwide, without anya costs*
See our productrange at www.singingrock.store
